   Lin, Chung-Ying and Chang, Yun-Hsuan and Hsieh, Yi-Ping and Lin,
   Yi-Ching and Herrera, Josue Jaru Ubeda and Tsai, Meng-Che},
Title = {Reciprocal Peer Network Processes on Substance Use and Delinquent
